Class CollectionAdapterTest<E>

java.lang.Object
CollectionAdapterTest<E>
public class CollectionAdapterTest<E>
extends java.lang.Object
Test Class for CollectionAdapter
Summary:
this class is in charge of testing the Collection class
Test Suite Design:
each individual method is tested, verifying that intermediate states are created and all of them are verified, to verify that the collection does not break during the editing
